Description
===========
If you need to fix Drupal permissions repeatedly then this script will help you,
it is based on the guidelines given on the reference handbook page and performs 
some checks before any modification to ensure it is not applied on files/directories outside your Drupal installation.

Usage
=====
$ chmod +x /path/to/permissioner.sh
$ su -c 'sh /path/to/permissioner.sh /path/to/drupal your_drupal_username'

Reference
=========
Securing file permissions and ownership <http://drupal.org/node/244924>

